    <p class="homepar">
        Northwest Labs Pharmaceutical provides chemical and compound tests for companies needing in-depth assay analysis.
    </p>
    <p><a class="btn btn-default btn-outline-dark" style ="font-size:25px;" href="@Url.Action("About", "Home")">Read more &raquo;</a></p>
</div>

<br />
<br />
